    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I do this. However I do not expose clearAll, nor could I figure out how to invoke it real quick, so maybe this doesn't help at all.\r\n\r\n```javascript\r\nvar search = instantsearch({\r\n\t    appId: 'x',\r\n\t    apiKey: 'x',\r\n\t    indexName: index_name,\r\n\t    urlSync: true,\r\n\t    searchParameters: {\r\n\t    \t    filters: \"name:\" + filters\r\n\t    }\r\n});\r\n```",
