    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "For now, default values should be added using `searchParameters` on the InstantSearch constructor. Values that can't be cleared should be implemented either using `filters` or implement a `searchFunction` that always add the value. There is more than one way to do that and it should be tailored on the usage, we should consider making that a guide.",
